</line><line>Apollo:
<textEffects>(Sounds like some kind of TV show. Things like that don't happen in real life.)</textEffects> ........................ ...Ah. Ahhhhhhhhhhhh!
</line><line>Phoenix:
A-Apollo! Did you just...?!
</line><line>Apollo:
