</line><line>Nahyuta:
<a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/d/d8/SoJ_Satorha%21.png/revision/latest?cb=20220420132507" class="image"><img alt="SoJ Satorha!" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="260" height="187" data-image-name="SoJ Satorha!.png" data-image-key="SoJ_Satorha%21.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/d/d8/SoJ_Satorha%21.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/260?cb=20220420132507" class="lazyload" /></a>
</line><line>Nahyuta:
