</line><line>Apollo:
I-I... That is... Nnnnnnrrrrrrrrgh! <textEffects>(What do you think you're doing, you idiot!)</textEffects>
</line><line>Ga'ran:
.........Truly, the truth can set us free.
</line><line>Phoenix:
