</line>


<line>Nahyuta:
And that is...?
</line><line>Apollo:
A file full of information that Dhurke collected on what happened twenty-three years ago. Of particular note right now is what's written here: "...<textEffects>the sins of the father are visited upon his children</textEffects>..." This deeply-held idea is why you were expelled from the royal family. Which means it wouldn't bode well for your sibling either... ...if <textEffects>she</textEffects> were revealed to be Dhurke's daughter.
</line><line>Nahyuta:
