</line><line>Apollo:
<textEffects>(Nahyuta... Is this really the new you? Resigning yourself to the will of another and killing any hope you held for the future... .........No! The Nahyuta I knew would never let himself be turned into this!)</textEffects>
</line><line>Nahyuta:
Now, Your Magistry, if you would hand down your verdict...
</line><line>Apollo:
<a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/1/15/English-_Objection%21_%28Animated%29_%28Transparent%29.gif/revision/latest?cb=20210111024459" class="image"><img alt="English- Objection! (Animated) (Transparent)" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="260" height="156" data-image-name="English- Objection! (Animated) (Transparent).gif" data-image-key="English-_Objection%21_%28Animated%29_%28Transparent%29.gif" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/aceattorney/images/1/15/English-_Objection%21_%28Animated%29_%28Transparent%29.gif/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/260?cb=20210111024459" class="lazyload" /></a>
</line><line>Apollo:
...You can say you're simply accepting your fate, Nahyuta... ...but I know that, deep down, there is still <textEffects>hope</textEffects> in your heart.
