</line>
<hr />
<line>Nahyuta:
Someday... ...he would come and free our family from the chains of the past. Perhaps, deep down... ...that is what I believed. I believed in Dhurke... our father.
</line><line>Apollo:
.........Nahyuta. I knew you--
</line><line>Nahyuta:
